Interface BasePreferenceForest.BaseNode<P,S extends java.util.stream.BaseStream<P,S>>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of elements representing propositional variables
    S - a stream type representing a branch
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IntPreferenceForest.Node, PreferenceForest.Node
    Enclosing interface:
    BasePreferenceForest<P,S extends java.util.stream.BaseStream<P,S>>

    public static interface BasePreferenceForest.BaseNode<P,S extends java.util.stream.BaseStream<P,S>>
    A node that stores an element of type P and a reference to its parent.
